reviewText: A very interesting thing is that we are not represented by our governments.  They fought the Jews in every way possible while the American people were in favor always of helping them.  This documentary glosses over the horrible behavior of the "free" governments of the world.
The story of Israel's birth as never portrayed before, or yet, since. Well narrated and beautifully depicted with rare, original footage.
Some is archival so there are grainy portions, but still an awesome story of Judaism and the state of Israel
